{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d8577975fe","title":"关于四十五军等部队行动部署致陶铸电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c3a47da6c7","index":0,"year":1951,"month":1,"day":22,"articleId":"d8577975fe"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dbcf15bd08","name":"陶铸","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"402349d3e2","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d8577975fe","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陶铸，当时任中共中央中南局常委、中国人民解放军中南军区政治部主任，被派往广西帮助工作。"},{"id":"58512647ee","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d8577975fe","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邓，指邓子恢，当时任中共中央中南局第三书记、中国人民解放军中南军区第二政治委员。谭，指谭政，当时任中共中央中南局副书记、中国人民解放军中南军区第三政治委员。叶，指叶剑英，当时任中共中央华南分局第一书记、中国人民解放军广东军区司令员兼政治委员。方，指方方，当时任中共中央华南分局第三书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"10619e27a5","type":"title","text":"关于四十五军等部队行动部署致陶铸电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d8577975fe"},{"id":"402349d3e2","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸同志，并告邓、谭，叶、方以：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d8577975fe"},{"id":"58512647ee","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十五日电悉。四十五军争取早日结束剩待命开韶关广州线整训备战；廿一兵团确定在广西境内期能及驻防；四十九军争取在五月或六月以后能集中使用，望按此意图进行部署","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d8577975fe"},{"id":"a967b2f7e5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d8577975fe"},{"id":"cec8cb807e","type":"paragraph","text":"一月廿二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d8577975fe"}],"page":{"id":"1239f5564d","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"d8577975fe","start":55,"end":55}}}},"__N_SSG":true}